OL,3,CPolice officer acquitted after tasered
OL,4,Csuspect left with life-changing
OL,5,Cinjuries
OL,7,FA police officer has been found not
OL,8,Fguilty of grevious bodily harm.
OL,10,FMetropolitan Police Constable Liam
OL,11,FNewman, 31, was accused of GBH against
OL,12,F61-year-old Leonard Sandiford who was
OL,13,Fseriously injured when he fell to the
OL,14,Fground after being tasered and now
OL,15,Fuses a wheelchair.
OL,17,FMr Sandiford was running away from
OL,18,Fpolice in Woodford Green, east London,
OL,19,Fwhen he reached a cul-de-sac and
OL,20,Fclimbed on an outbuilding.
