OL,3,CPolice officer acquitted after tasered
OL,4,Csuspect left with life-changing
OL,5,Cinjuries
OL,7,FNewman had been with another officer
OL,8,Fresponding to a report of attempted
OL,9,Fburglary of a bookmaker in Chigwell
OL,10,FRoad, Woodford Green, at 5am on April
OL,11,F24 2022.
OL,13,FBody-worn video footage was played to
OL,14,Fthe jury which showed Mr Sandiford
OL,15,Fmoving across the outbuilding with his
OL,16,Fback to the camera, and the Taser
OL,17,Fbeing pointed and activated, before Mr
OL,18,FSandiford disappears from view.
