OL,3,CPolice officer acquitted after tasered
OL,4,Csuspect left with life-changing
OL,5,Cinjuries
OL,7,FAfter being called to Chigwell Road,
OL,8,Fthe two officers approached a white
OL,9,FFord van driven by Mr Sandiford and
OL,10,Fcut it off as it approached a side
OL,11,Froad, the court was told earlier in
OL,12,Fthe trial.
OL,14,FThe officers tried to stop the vehicle
OL,15,Fand Newman used his baton to strike at
OL,16,Fthe driver's side, opened the driver's
OL,17,Fdoor and tried to pull Mr Sandiford
OL,18,Fout, the court heard.
