OL,3,CPolice officer acquitted after tasered
OL,4,Csuspect left with life-changing
OL,5,Cinjuries
OL,7,FNewman said it was his "honest belief"
OL,8,FMr Sandiford was "trying to run me
OL,9,Fover" during the incident but that he
OL,10,Fnow accepts this was not the case.
OL,12,FMr Sandiford previously told the court
OL,13,Fhe had run from the officers because
OL,14,Fhe had been "spooked" after seeing a
OL,15,Ftruncheon and a Taser.
OL,17,FNewman pleaded not guilty on 20
OL,18,FNovember 2024 following the
OL,19,Finvestigation by the Independent
OL,20,FOffice for Police Conduct (IOPC).
