OL,4,Csuspect left with life-changing
OL,5,Cinjuries
OL,7,FChief Superintendent Stuart Bell, who
OL,8,Fis responsible for policing in
OL,9,FRedbridge, said: "Our thoughts today
OL,10,Fare with Mr Sandiford who has been
OL,11,Fleft with life-changing injuries
OL,12,Ffollowing this tragic incident.
OL,14,F"It is always a matter of huge regret
OL,15,Fwhen an individual comes to harm
OL,16,Ffollowing contact with police and
OL,17,Fvital that in such circumstances
OL,18,Fofficers be held to the highest level
OL,19,Fof scrutiny.
