OL,7,F"They face challenging situations
OL,8,Feveryday and have to make difficult
OL,9,Fdecisions in the moment.
OL,11,F"We understand the concern caused by
OL,12,Fincidents of this nature and will be
OL,13,Fworking with our local residents,
OL,14,Fpartner agencies, and key members of
OL,15,Fthose communities directly affected to
OL,16,Funderstand any impact and provide
OL,17,Fsupport.
